kpi_info.use: Number of failed Inter System Handover preparations to UTRAN due to other reasons of target cell per neighbor cell relationship. UPDATED: Updated when an S1AP:HANDOVER PREPARATION FAILURE message is received from MME with other cause than "No radio resources available in target cell" for an Inter System Handover. This counter is updated for the source cell of the handover.
